Additional models of NC316W, NC316P, NC326PW, NC326P, NC326W defined in the FCC test report.
The schematics state the device has 8MB Flash and 128MB RAM.
The NC326W appears to be filed under '''Shenzhen Baolongsheng Technology''''s grantee code (FCC ID: S6UBLSIPCAM) :"ABNC3161VD" is silkscreened on the main board. ::'''Grain''' GM8126SF-QC SoC ::'''Samsung''' K4T51163QJ (K4T51163QJ-BCE7?) 64MB RAM :"JW801M0 Ver:1.3" is silkscreened on the wireless module board. "JW-8XXMN" is on the label affixed to the module's shield. :"ABNC316IR1VB" is silkscreened on the IR light board. :"ABNC326OV97151VA" is silkscreened on the sensor module.
Default settings are per the FCC manual. :The default SSID appears to be '''wirelessnc''' (w/ Ad-Hoc mode).
